The first portable stereo made up of a cassette player plus headphones,

72
00:05:26,319 --> 00:05:29,120
pairs of padded speakers worn over the ears.

73
00:05:29,120 --> 00:05:34,079
Sony Chairman Ekiyomarita was so confident his invention would take off,

74
00:05:34,079 --> 00:05:38,079
become popular and successful that he laid his job on the line.

75
